parameters: Ladies and gentlemen, citizens of The Underground!
What you are about to witness will be a bloodbath of man versus zombie!
Only the strongest competitors will have a chance to survive.
And should a competitor emerge victorious from this onslaught...
They will receive a congratulatory 'service' from one of my own ladies.
I'm sure you all know my ladies don't come cheap...
Now!\! It's time to begin our first round!
This first competitor is a brand new face in The Underground.
He's short, but he's sure to pack a punch.
\n<Crowd>This guy will get ripped to shreds!
I'll show you guys who's gonna be the next champ!
Against all odds, a survivor has emerged victorious in The Colosseum!
Give it up for \n[1]!\! Semi-finalist of The Violet Cup!
All of the other competitors have either cowered in defeat or gotten ripped to shreds by zombies.
As you all know, there can only ever be one winner in The Colosseum.
Our other semi-finalist, the mysterious boy from outside the city.\! Come on out!
Now the two of you will face off to the death in a bloody fight for the crown.
Residents of The Underground!\! This will be the show of the century!
L-Look, I don't think we should-
The winner of the Violet Cup is \n[1]!
To think a rookie could clear The Violet Cup and still remain standing!
Ladies and gentleman, give it up for \n[1]!
\n<Crowd>I always knew you could do it \n[1]!
At least now they believe in me!
